  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565893131-6H24VHH8O2W5XGQQQ4DJ/6a-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>We are bursting with excitement over here 💕  This has been in the works since last summer and it's finally here! Well, almost... The new <a href=\"http://bit.ly/amyplannerpouch\">Planner Pouch</a> is now available for pre-order!! </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6b-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565931201-N1C026H0YA9XS4KEBAFN/6b-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"6c-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565932868-W1NR56E9805YBPE3LECY/6c-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6d-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565934097-RPH0QQXJY7NJRHECI8Q9/6d-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6e-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565941422-00URF20VRQTY31H20KWR/6e-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6f-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565945381-F97Y7RP7PGTBQ9QK57VS/6f-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6g-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565946924-W3Q493ECMXYMUTT3D4ZC/6g-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>We designed it so it’s perfectly sized to fit your favorite supplies including pens, stickers, and even an A5 <a href=\"http://amzn.to/2EEMWtv\">bullet journal</a>! And for those who asked, <a href=\"https://shop.amytangerine.com/shop/traveler-s-notebook-inserts\">traveler's notebooks</a> also fit in it! Use it for planning and memory-keeping on the go - or whatever you want - and fill it with all the good stuff.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"6h-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565965375-QGDUXL6FDADOKNTSHOPP/6h-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6i-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565967188-TAN37JZUIPY5ME5228BH/6i-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"6j-Amy+Tangerine+Planner+Pouch+_+Now+Available+for+Pre-Sale!.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565969340-H4YUXZXLORJ4NUMUCNO0/6j-Amy%2BTangerine%2BPlanner%2BPouch%2B_%2BNow%2BAvailable%2Bfor%2BPre-Sale%21.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http://bit.ly/amyplannerpouch\">Planner pouches</a> will begin shipping at the end of February, but all pre-orders placed before 2/20 will receive the cutest mini rainbow washi tape!</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1590565993052-1CLCR3S3KNGB3X85AOSL/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>If you have any questions, leave them below and I will try and shoot a YouTube video with the answers. I can't wait to see how you put your own <a href=\"http://bit.ly/amyplannerpouch\">planner pouch</a> to use!</p>"
